  "khoj-aio" = {
    description = "Beginner-friendly All-in-One Unraid container for Khoj, a self-hosted AI second brain. Bundles the Khoj web app with an internal PostgreSQL database in a single container, while still supporting local or hosted LLMs, external search backends, reverse proxies, and advanced power-user overrides."
